text: Howard George (February 6, 1935 - February 24, 2010) was an American wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman light heavyweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:2010 deaths Category:American male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the United States Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Watertown, New York
